steps to maintain workflow translations:

1) Access to tcode SE63.

2) From Menu: select Translation --> ABAP Objects --> Transport Object

3) Enter transport data:

- R3TR PDWS [Object ID] for Workflow Template

- R3TR PDTS [Object ID] for Standard Task

4) Select Source and Target Language (I suppose Source EN, Target IT)

5) Clic Edit button

6) Translate available texts.

7) Add translations to a Workbench request with RS_LXE_RECORD_TORDER report

8) Release Transport request.
